### Test API - Get Pending Payments (All branches)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/invoices/payments/pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test API - Get Pending Payments (Specific branch)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/invoices/payments/pending?branchId=1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test API - Count Pending Payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/invoices/payments/pending/count
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
